  (str content) (str `[Amendment of Act 63 of 1951.] Rep. by s. 2 and the First Schedule, ibid. (w.e.f. 31-3-1988).`)
  (str footnotes) (str )
  (str query) (str abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_2_11_00051_198348_1517807326456&sectionId=32533&sectionno=6&orderno=6&orgactid=AC_CEN_2_11_00051_198348_1517807326456)
